<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="Dendrocopos_minor#cite_ref-11">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text">HBV (1994) Bd.&#160;9, S.&#160;1098</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-12"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="Dendrocopos_minor#cite_ref-12">↑</a></span> <span class="reference-text">Dvorak (1993) S.&#160;267</span></li>
